"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"I believe Heroes of Mavia, the next generation mass-multiplayer strategy game with sustainable play-to-earn economics,has the potential to be the best blockchain game in 2022. My reasons come from four aspects, Game playability, economic model, Technical strength and community affinity.\\n\\n**1.Game playability.**\\n\\nThe poor quality of the first generation of blockchain games was widely criticized, and most of them had no playability. play2earn must be transformed into play&earn. Mavia has excellent gameplay comparable to traditional Online Multiplayer Strategy games.Attack and defeat rival bases by strategically timing and placing troops in battle. Each plot of land is an NFT with a unique design and location on the Mavia island.Choose from dozens of different air, vehicle and infantry troops to lead your army to victory against rival bases. Structure your defensive buildings, troops and traps to defend your base against opponents.\\n\\n**2.Economic model.**\\n\\nOne of the main issues many blockchain-based games are experiencing is hyperinflation of their play-to-earn currencies. In the first generation of blockchain games, the fragile economic model is its biggest dead end. The economic collapse of famous games such as raca and cryptominer has Serious impact on market confidence. Mavia use economic models which they process and test using hundreds of simulations, ensuring the resilience and balance of all sectors of the ecosystem.Mavias development team spent countless hours refining and simulating the economic model to support a sustainable growth model for RUBY. With over 10 deflationary paths for currency, supported by deep integration of currency utility into the gameplay of Mavia, I believe they have developed one of the most durable economic models in crypto gaming.\\n\\n**3.Technical strength.**\\n\\nMavia is built on the Ethereum blockchain, utilizing Arbitrum as an L2 scaling solution. The MAVIA token can be bridged between ETH L1 and Arbitrum L2 by using the Mavia bridge. Binance Smart Chain support will be coming to the Mavia bridge in the near future.All of their game content is designed and developed from scratch, from conceptual designs to 3D character modeling and animations. Also they are building long-term infrastructure for other Blockchain-based games.\\n\\n**4.community affinity.**\\n\\nMavia has one of the best blockchain gaming communities, not only the most degen crypto investors, but also sincere gamers. Not like other games require expensive admission tickets, making the game a financial game for a few people, Mavia open to the largest group of users even they can't afford expensive games, they do not need to own land outright to be able to play in Mavia, They could enjoy the game by renting and partnerships require no upfront payment.This preserves the diversity of the player base, thereby guarantee of the robustness of the game system.\\n\\nFor more information,please check:\\n\\n* **Official Mavia Website**: <https://www.mavia.com/>\\n* **Official Mavia Twitter**: <https://twitter.com/MaviaGame>\\n* **Official Mavia Youtube**: <https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCEsG9bqZilH29cW6gC5oApQ>\\n* **Official Mavia Medium**: <https://medium.com/heroes-of-mavia>\\n* **Official Mavia Instagram**: <https://www.instagram.com/heroesofmavia/>\",\"timestamp\":1642269709,\"title\":\"Why I think Heroes of Mavia has the potential to be the best blockchain game of 2022 \"},\"digest\":\"D0UVDaxabTt9GL0OwRam0HMr4mTUAHvo-I3a-mKCSRY\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x154a309479E3CC5B40A363a419262601b9502B40\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"qbTJx8FvbVLRKhiYT_NBkJiGzAmGif2fDlr7JrL7M90\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"rubBXACOjhAaoz5Y68TZm8B1sfn2e3Y842Le0TWiomk\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"nVwfNfHylrPcxMSncVFe60ZUytQ3ouYEZlXyqso17n-v0ec63_Ov0jOMTHzHlfyJeeoXaEPbIftJ_oZk-xqOew\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x76b52e7e3